			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="7" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="When players, as the Dark Urge, accept a duel with Orin. And the companions honour the deal of not getting involved in the battle. And the DU was defeated by Orin.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;This dialog will start. Upon which Orin will want to sacrifice the remaining players with the rest of the temple." />
